#: ../../hardware/controllers/allen_heath_xone_k2_k1.md:4
msgid "Allen & Heath Xone:K1/K2/K3"
msgstr ""

#: ../../hardware/controllers/allen_heath_xone_k2_k1.md:7
msgid ""
"The Allen & Heath Xone:K2 is a flexible controller that is mapped to control"
" Mixxx’s decks, effects, or both. It has an integrated 4 channel audio "
"interface with 2 RCA jacks and an 1/8\" stereo headphone jack. The Xone K1 "
"is the same as the Xone K2 but without the built in audio interface and does"
" not come with the EVA travel case that the K2 comes with. The Xone K3 works"
" with the same mapping after updating its firmware to v1.0.4 r 93846."
msgstr ""

